  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if the frequency of blood glucose testing in patients with type 2 diabetes who
      are being treated with diet and exercise alone or diet and exercise plus oral agents will
      impact the HbA1c level.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine the impact of SMBG frequency on blood glucose control in patients receiving
      systematic diabetes management education through Type 2 Diabetes BASICS at International
      Diabetes Center.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
